title: The 40K Collection, v3.0
description:
A biger and better collection of all of the 40K .stl files on the interwebs, snagged before GW can spoil the fun. Formerly known as the Garin Collection, since he made most of the Tyranid and Terminator files.

v3.0, as of 5/11/2014

Contains the following:

General
-Scatter die and templates

Apocalypse
-Knight Paladin Titan
-Tyranid Bio-Titan
-Imperial Knight

Epic:
-Buildings

Variety of city and ship corridor bases

Imperial Guard:
-Leman Russ tank
-Sentinel
-Saber Defense Platform
-Chimera
-Manticore

Necrons:
-Monolith
-Warrior

Orks:
-Orks
-Orc conversion kit for other models
-Grotzooka and Deffkopta Bigbomb
-Grot artillery
-Scrap Barricades
-Killa Kan

Chaos:
-Elphias the Inheritor
-Chaos marine

Necromunda:
-Weapons

Space Marines:
-Various Torsoes, bodies, and arms/legs
-Space Hulk Terminators
-Various weapons
-Bikes, and bike-riding models
-Dreadnoughts (Model and weapon options)
-Drop pods
-Grek Knight Terminator captain
-Various Primarchs
-Terminators and weapon options
-Centurions w/50mm bases
-One-piece marines
-Female marines (One-piece)
-Caestus Assault Ram
-Predator
-Land Raider
-Land Speeder
-Hippo APC/tanks
-Vindicator

Tau
-Drone body
-Crisis Battlesuit

Tyranids:
-Termagaunts
-Carnifex
-Zoanthrope
-Hive Tyrant
-Tervigon
-Lictor
-Warrior
-Hormagaunt
-Adrenal Glands
-Genestealers
-Biovore
-Ripper

Enjoy, and fuck GW!
